00:09:04.760 --> 00:09:07.140
to celebrate this 2018 Class

00:09:07.140 --> 00:09:09.920
of the National Student
Poets Program.

00:09:09.920 --> 00:09:13.330
We are extremely proud to have
partnered with the Alliance

00:09:13.330 --> 00:09:16.420
for Young Artists and Writers
to establish the program

00:09:16.420 --> 00:09:20.170
which shares exemplary
work from teen poets

00:09:20.170 --> 00:09:24.410
like those we honor today,
with a national audience.

00:09:24.410 --> 00:09:28.030
As you well know, IMLS
also supports libraries

00:09:28.030 --> 00:09:31.020
and museums large and
small across the country

00:09:31.020 --> 00:09:33.770
as they enhance many
forms of literacy

00:09:33.770 --> 00:09:38.420
and artistic expression,
including this poetry program.

00:09:38.420 --> 00:09:41.980
Writing and libraries of
course, are always intertwined

00:09:41.980 --> 00:09:45.950
as I was reminded of this
last week when up in Maine.

00:09:45.950 --> 00:09:47.880
I had been telling
my Maine friends

00:09:47.880 --> 00:09:50.400
about upcoming activities
at IMLS.

00:09:50.400 --> 00:09:54.630
I can't turn off my brain
about libraries and museums.

00:09:54.630 --> 00:09:57.570
Including this Poetry
Celebration.

00:09:57.570 --> 00:10:00.230
The next day my friend
was driving me on one

00:10:00.230 --> 00:10:03.490
of those endless
winding Maine roads.

00:10:03.490 --> 00:10:06.690
My friend suddenly turned
the Jeep of the road,

00:10:06.690 --> 00:10:11.630
through a battered chain link
fence into a small cemetery.

00:10:11.630 --> 00:10:13.910
The grass was try, scruffy

00:10:13.910 --> 00:10:16.920
and there were few
graveside decorations.

00:10:16.920 --> 00:10:21.350
It seemed utilitarian
and in fact ignored.

00:10:21.350 --> 00:10:22.690
At the very back edge

00:10:22.690 --> 00:10:27.240
of the cemetery was a very
non-descript plot under a tree.

00:10:27.240 --> 00:10:29.820
Elwin Brooks White.

00:10:29.820 --> 00:10:33.130
Various votives,
rocks, paper sculptures,

00:10:33.130 --> 00:10:37.050
folded notes were perched
on the simple headstone.

00:10:37.050 --> 00:10:39.930
Many of White's books
and artworks were donated

00:10:39.930 --> 00:10:44.490
to the nearby Friend Memorial
Library in Brooklyn, Maine.

00:10:44.490 --> 00:10:46.460
One book inscription reads

00:10:46.460 --> 00:10:48.960
for the Friend Memorial
Public Library

00:10:48.960 --> 00:10:52.760
from a long-time
admirer E.B. White.

00:10:52.760 --> 00:10:55.460
And in a letter addressed
to the children of Troy,

00:10:55.460 --> 00:10:59.180
Michigan congratulating them
upon their newly opened public

00:10:59.180 --> 00:11:03.610
library, E.B. White
wrote, Books hold many

00:11:03.610 --> 00:11:05.800
of the secrets of the world.

00:11:05.800 --> 00:11:07.230
Books are people.

00:11:07.230 --> 00:11:10.830
People who have managed
to stay alive by hiding

00:11:10.830 --> 00:11:12.290
between the covers of a book.

00:11:12.290 --> 00:11:17.260
And we can say the same of
poetry as White did of books.

00:11:17.260 --> 00:11:21.250
Poetry holds many of the
secrets of the world,

00:11:21.250 --> 00:11:25.800
and people stay alive
within and through poetry.

00:11:25.800 --> 00:11:27.510
Many libraries and museums

00:11:27.510 --> 00:11:30.000
across our nation are
critical platforms

00:11:30.000 --> 00:11:33.450
for community expression
and advancing literacy

00:11:33.450 --> 00:11:35.260
and learning for all Americans.

00:11:35.260 --> 00:11:39.710
And the National Student Poets
Program leverages these shared

00:11:39.710 --> 00:11:43.330
community spaces to
create new perspectives,

00:11:43.330 --> 00:11:46.830
connect us across
generations, and spark critical

00:11:46.830 --> 00:11:50.280
and essential conversations.

00:11:50.280 --> 00:11:54.720
This year's five exceptional
student writers, Darius, Daniel,

00:11:54.720 --> 00:11:58.540
Alexandra, Heather and
Ariana were selected by some

00:11:58.540 --> 00:12:03.050
of our nation's finest literary
voices and leaders in education.

00:12:03.050 --> 00:12:08.550
And they rose to the top of more
than 300 national medalists.

00:12:08.550 --> 00:12:10.200
That's a feat.

00:12:10.200 --> 00:12:13.320
In the scholastic art
and writing awards.

00:12:13.320 --> 00:12:16.700
They will receive academic
awards, opportunities

00:12:16.700 --> 00:12:20.530
to showcase their work in
libraries, museums, schools

00:12:20.530 --> 00:12:23.450
and at festivals and
events across America.

00:12:23.450 --> 00:12:27.390
And they'll serve as
regional literary ambassadors

00:12:27.390 --> 00:12:29.530
for the coming year.

00:12:29.530 --> 00:12:32.860
Each student poet from this
year's class is charged

00:12:32.860 --> 00:12:36.210
with designing a special
community service project

00:12:36.210 --> 00:12:40.130
which may include readings,
workshops, webinars,

00:12:40.130 --> 00:12:43.110
classroom visit's,
interviews and conversations

00:12:43.110 --> 00:12:45.210
with established poets.

00:12:45.210 --> 00:12:47.890
In previous years young
writers have chosen

00:12:47.890 --> 00:12:51.130
to focus their efforts on
outreach and engagement

00:12:51.130 --> 00:12:54.870
with military families,
Alzheimer's patients,

00:12:54.870 --> 00:12:57.810
English as second language
students, homeless youth

00:12:57.810 --> 00:13:00.040
and Native American students.

00:13:00.040 --> 00:13:02.360
And I really look forward
to hearing how each

00:13:02.360 --> 00:13:04.320
of you will reach out to others.

00:13:04.320 --> 00:13:06.550
This is just the beginning.

00:13:06.550 --> 00:13:10.970
Whether reading E.B. White or
participating in a poetry slam,

00:13:10.970 --> 00:13:13.530
I truly believe anyone
can own the power

00:13:13.530 --> 00:13:15.880
of poetry and have a voice.

00:13:15.880 --> 00:13:19.630
Our five winning poets are
ambassadors for poetry's power

00:13:19.630 --> 00:13:24.880
to inspire curiosity, learning
confidence and connections.

00:13:24.880 --> 00:13:28.040
I want to congratulate you
on your accomplishments,

00:13:28.040 --> 00:13:31.070
and we look forward to your
continued service throughout the

00:13:31.070 --> 00:13:32.370
next year.

00:13:32.370 --> 00:13:34.170
Thank you.

