00:29:25.680 --> 00:29:42.040
but you're out in the cold
and you're feeling empty,

00:29:42.040 --> 00:29:46.860
are you looking for somebody.

00:29:46.860 --> 00:29:50.630
Would I be somebody?

00:29:50.630 --> 00:29:53.870
Somebody to love.

00:29:53.870 --> 00:30:00.370
Would I be somebody, would I
be somebody, I be somebody.

00:30:00.370 --> 00:30:10.110
Would I be somebody,
would I be somebody,

00:30:10.110 --> 00:30:17.840
would I be somebody,
somebody to love.

00:30:17.840 --> 00:30:23.550
Are you watching the moon
rise in the darkness of night,

00:30:23.550 --> 00:30:35.530
and battered and broken
