00:30:35.530 --> 00:30:44.580
You ain't got nobody.

00:30:44.580 --> 00:30:46.820
Would I be somebody.

00:30:46.820 --> 00:30:50.020
Somebody to love.

00:30:50.020 --> 00:30:59.560
Would I be somebody, I would
be somebody, I be somebody.

00:30:59.560 --> 00:31:07.470
Would I be somebody, I be
somebody, I be somebody,

00:31:07.470 --> 00:31:10.800
would I be somebody,
I be somebody,

00:31:10.800 --> 00:31:18.510
I be some body, somebody
to love.

00:31:18.510 --> 00:31:25.510
[ Music ]

00:31:25.510 --> 00:31:33.040
[ Applause ]

00:31:33.040 --> 00:31:35.750
She's a sweet baby.

00:31:35.750 --> 00:31:39.240
So I'd like to invite the
