00:32:06.490 --> 00:32:09.530
And representing the
Northeast is Alexandra

00:32:09.530 --> 00:32:17.630
Contreras-Montesano, let me
know I know I messed that up.

00:32:17.630 --> 00:32:23.550
And representing the Southwest
