00:48:31.730 --> 00:48:34.000
I'm the Programs Manager at the
Poetry and Literature Center

00:48:34.000 --> 00:48:35.720
and the task falls
on me to close

00:48:35.720 --> 00:48:37.620
out these beautiful festivities.

00:48:37.620 --> 00:48:39.810
But before I do, I want to
see if we can play this video.

00:48:39.810 --> 00:48:41.450
I'm told that we
